### ============================================================
###  S03-26 Web App — Analytics API
###  Base URL: http://localhost:3001
###  Usar con la extensión REST Client (VS Code)
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001

### [1] Obtener estadísticas del Dashboard (7 días por defecto)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Obtener estadísticas del Dashboard (rango personalizado)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/dashboard?range=15
Accept: application/json

###

### [3] Obtener mensajes en el tiempo (7 días)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/messages-over-time
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Obtener mensajes en el tiempo (30 días)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/messages-over-time?range=30
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Obtener actividad reciente (últimos 5 registros)
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/recent-activity
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Obtener toda la actividad
GET {{baseUrl}}/analytics/recent-activity/all
Accept: application/json